  "translations": {
    "en": "Umm Ayman visited the Prophet (may Allah bless him and his family) and she had something in her coat. So the Messenger of Allah (may Allah bless him and his family) said to her: What do you have with you, O Umm Ayman? She said: Indeed, so-and-so got married, and they sprinkled things upon her, and I took some of what was sprinkled. Then Umm Ayman wept and said: O Messenger of Allah, you married Fatima off but did not sprinkle anything on her.",
